                     <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY</hi>.<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy by the Jury, on the ground that he was not aware of the serious crime he was committing</hi>
                  </rs>.— <rs id="t18661119-56-punishment-57" type="punishmentDescription">
